"""
smart-ask: AI task router with v3 cascade gates

  Gate 1  Gemini classifier — easy/hard structural check
  Gate 2  Quick Gemini draft — code smell check on actual output
  Gate 3  Visible doctest check — run >>> examples from prompt

  easy (all gates pass) → gemini-2.5-flash-lite via Hermes
  hard (any gate fails) → claude-opus-4.8       via Hermes

Saves ~53% cost vs always-Opus with <3pp accuracy loss.
"""

